<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FIR Draft</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 1in;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 6.5in;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24pt;
            margin-bottom: 0.5in;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 0.2in;
        }
        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .underline {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 0.75in;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            width: 3in;
            margin-top: 0.2in;
            padding-top: 0.05in;
        }
        .date-place {
            margin-top: 0.5in;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 1in;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>First Information Report (FIR) Draft</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <p>To,</p>
            <p>The Station House Officer,</p>
            <p><span class="bold underline">{{ police_station | default("[Name of Police Station]") }}</span>,</p>
            <p><span class="bold underline">{{ police_station_address | default("[Address of Police Station]") }}</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">Subject:</span> Regarding <span class="bold underline">{{ subject | default("[Nature of Complaint, e.g., Theft, Assault, Cheating]") }}</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Respected Sir/Madam,</p>
            <p>I, <span class="bold underline">{{ complainant_name | default("[Complainant's Full Name]") }}</span>, son/daughter/wife of <span class="bold underline">{{ complainant_father_name | default("[Complainant's Father/Husband's Name]") }}</span>, residing at <span class="bold underline">{{ complainant_address | default("[Complainant's Full Address]") }}</span>, Mobile No. <span class="bold underline">{{ complainant_contact | default("[Complainant's Mobile Number]") }}</span>, wish to lodge a complaint regarding the following incident:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">Date of Incident:</span> <span class="underline">{{ incident_date | default("[Date of Incident]") }}</span></p>
            <p><span class="bold">Time of Incident:</span> <span class="underline">{{ incident_time | default("[Time of Incident]") }}</span></p>
            <p><span class="bold">Place of Incident:</span> <span class="underline">{{ incident_location | default("[Location of Incident]") }}</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">Facts of the Incident:</span></p>
            <p>{{ facts_of_incident | default("[Detailed description of the incident, including what happened, how it happened, and who was involved (if known).]") }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">Accused (if known):</span> <span class="underline">{{ accused_name | default("[Name of Accused, if known]") }}</span>, son/daughter of <span class="underline">{{ accused_father_name | default("[Accused's Father/Husband's Name, if known]") }}</span>, residing at <span class="underline">{{ accused_address | default("[Accused's Address, if known]") }}</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">Stolen/Lost Items (if any):</span> {{ stolen_items | default("[List of stolen/lost items with descriptions, e.g., 'One Samsung Galaxy S23, Black, IMEI: XXXXXXXXXX']") }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><span class="bold">Witness Details (if any):</span> {{ witness_details | default("[Names and contact details of any witnesses]") }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>I request you to kindly register my complaint as an FIR and take necessary legal action against the culprits. I am ready to provide any further information or assistance required for the investigation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-block">
            <p>Yours faithfully,</p>
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <p class="bold">{{ complainant_name | default("[Complainant's Full Name]") }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="date-place">
            <p>Date: {{ current_date }}</p>
            <p>Place: {{ place | default("[Place]") }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
